Uses of Package
net.myorb.math.matrices

  • Packages that use net.myorb.math.matrices 
    Package Description
    net.myorb.math.characteristics
    Eigenvalue and eigenvector primitive descriptions and implementations.
    net.myorb.math.computational
    Support for computation in multiple dimensions mostly focused on calculus.
    net.myorb.math.expressions
    Core set of classes supporting representation of expressions and their evaluations.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.algorithms
    Implementations of algorithms that provide for evaluation of expression primitives.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.commands
    Implementations of the command interface for groups of associated commands.
    net.myorb.math.linalg
    Linear Algebra algorithm implementations for solutions to equation sets.
    net.myorb.math.matrices
    Representations for Vectors and Matricies and implementations of their arithmetic operators.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.cofactors
    Support for computation of Matrix cofactors (brute force and improved efficiency).
    net.myorb.math.matrices.colt
    Data abstraction translation between CalcLib and the Colt library.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.optimization
    Implementations of algorithms supporting efficient computation of Matrix cofactors.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.slices
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Matrix slice concepts.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.transforms
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Householder and Von Mises transforms.
    net.myorb.math.vanche
    Data representations supporting implementation of VanChe linear algebra concepts.
    net.myorb.testing
    Implementations of algorithms supporting CalcLib unit tests.
